return "return {[\"background\"] = \"gui_hobbitbg.png\", " ..
	"[\"title\"] = \"Mystic Rods\"," ..
	"[\"page_max\"] = 11, [\"text_len\"] = 2000, [\"owner\"] = \"an unknown author\"," ..
	"[\"text\"] = \"Rods are magic items that grant a special power. Each require a rod base and a white, red, purple, or blue gem. The gem must be mined, prepared, cut, and polished according to the designs of the elvish ringsmiths. The two pieces are then fused together in a dual furnace. Using rods requires a substantial amount of magical power (mana).\\\n\\\n" ..
	"There are four rods that can be crafted:\\\n\\\n" ..
	"\\\n\\\nROD OF HEALING - White Gem\\\n\\\n" ..
	"The Rod of Healing instantly heals you for five health, and players in a medium-range beam for six health!\\\n\\\n" ..
	"\\\n\\\nROD OF DEFENSE - Blue Gem\\\n\\\n" ..
	"The Rod of Defense summons a random guardian from the list below. If a guard is already under your control and in visual range, using the rod again will teleport your guard to you.  If your guard is not visible and you use the rod again, it will be dismissed.\\\n\\\n" ..
	"You may right click a guardian to customize it's behavior. All guardians attack evil monsters on sight.\\\n\\\n" ..
	"Your guardians are dismissed when you log out. They will not remain in the world forever, and will eventually vanish. The guardian types are:\\\n\\\n" ..
	"Wolf: Fast and ravenously hungry, its huge jaws will attack your enemies, but fur isn't very good armor...\\\n\\\n" ..
	"Elf: Uses powerful elven magic to attack from a distance, but fragile\\\n\\\n" ..
	"Dwarf: Durable, mithril-clad warrior, but rather slow\\\n\\\n" ..
	"Soldier: A soldier of Rohan equipped with great armor. Uses a spear to attack at a large range, but not as tough as a dwarf. Both the dwarf and soldier guardians are vulnerable to fire.\\\n\\\n"..
	"ROD OF POLYMORPH - Red Gem\\\n\\\n" ..
	"The mighty elven ring of power, Vilya, grants powers of movement and levitation. However, the Rod of Polymorph can also grant these things in its own fashion by transforming you for a short time.\\\n\\\n" ..
	"NORMAL USE - Rabbit: Grants great speed and powerful jump for a short time\\\n\\\n" ..
	"SNEAK + CLICK - Butterfly: Grants flight\\\n\\\n" ..
	"ROD OF DOOM - Purple Gem\\\n\\\n" ..
	"This powerful rod paralyzes and blinds players caught in the beam, rendering them helpless for a short time.  Monsters take massive damage instead, killing most in one shot.  The secondary function transforms you into a ghost!\\\n\\\n\"}"
